<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I would recommend The Longest Ride and The Last Song. I say the Longest Ride is the happiest of Spark&apos;s novels I have read. Even though there is trage<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I would recommend The Longest Ride and The Last Song. I say the Longest Ride is the happiest of Spark's novels I have read. Even though there is tragedy, it has positive tone. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
