        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3875688102" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8640448054926690202">A wonderfully unfolding love story that took me inside Adrienne&apos;s life and heart and is my favorite of Nicholas Sparks&apos; novels. I love the letters that reveal so much of the story. Read it in two sittings and couldn&apos;t put it down. Just finished my 3rd reading of it in 10 years. Still holding it and gazing at the shining moonlit horizon on the beautiful cover with moist eyes.</span>
  <span id="freeText8640448054926690202" style="display:none">A wonderfully unfolding love story that took me inside Adrienne's life and heart and is my favorite of Nicholas Sparks' novels. I love the letters that reveal so much of the story. Read it in two sittings and couldn't put it down. Just finished my 3rd reading of it in 10 years. Still holding it and gazing at the shining moonlit horizon on the beautiful cover with moist eyes.</span>
  <a data-text-id="8640448054926690202" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
